{"tid":176360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"情場失意,事業也失意","createTime":"2017-03-28T06:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T08:27:58.000Z","uid":45142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d71698386cde4335a3122823cf141cea22616803","tid":176360,"uid":45142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣，出世到以家都未拖過女仔既手，更唔好提KISS。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年都21, 一直抱住姜太公釣魚願者上鉤既心態。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到以家０人approach，我係唔係要跳樓死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到Ｄ ＭＫ仔左擁右抱，葡萄到死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利串：　冇女仔肯同我主動講野"},{"pid":"305a17e0c0b1f682a79d612d2fee91349b76ff62","tid":176360,"uid":45142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:02:30.000Z","msg":"竟然冇巴打同我有一樣的遭遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185c03606a04bae16483953933094fb4c450b3b1","tid":176360,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2592bd978c91fc243fbb3e25268825c5e4acbcd","tid":176360,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:17:13.000Z","msg":"21歲就叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56bcbd8aef2865c82d8d8afbd34c2471756594d","tid":176360,"uid":45142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:27:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>21歲就叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔想叫春。<br />\n開頭我覺得冇女冇咩問題，but自從我堂弟帶左女女見家長，我就開始成日比人抽水。開始覺得自己好失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}